title: Minimal Contribution from International Tourism
description: In 2019, Guinea-Bissau's international tourism receipts for passenger transport items were among the lowest globally, amounting to just $19,999.99.

title: High Dependency on Food Imports
description: In 2018, food imports constituted 41.71% of Guinea-Bissau's total merchandise imports, indicating a significant reliance on foreign food sources.

title: Negligible Manufacturing Export Sector
description: In 2015, manufactured goods made up a mere 0.00009% of Guinea-Bissau's merchandise exports, highlighting a minimal manufacturing industry.
